| ------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Data          | Fix ImageFolder directory structure                       |
| Model         | Increase `hidden_size` to at least 256â€“512                |
| Model         | Use `BCEWithLogitsLoss()` and remove `Sigmoid()` in `D`   |
